Design the data model so it can represent what major PMS platforms represent:
- People, companies, staff
- Many-to-many relationships between contacts and matters with role semantics
- Custom fields and configurable sections
- Communications logs (email/call/sms) linked to contacts + matters
- Flexible matter pipelines + practice areas + statuses
- External system IDs for migration/sync

